metadata.name: Rye is ripe
metadata.description:
This is 1 NFT from my grandfather collection of paintings, that have been issued as a single, unique edition.

image size: 12802x9420 px

The original painting size 90x70cm 
oil on canvas
The village near Moscow where grandfather liked to go for plein air. He painted his sketches there which became the basis for this painting.

*price for nft only
